Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.clientstates

Abstract classes defining the possible states of the Client. Each class: - provides methods that implement UI-independent functionalities - provides attributes that are meant to be filled by the UI with the values obtained from the user - must be extended by a UI-specific class that implements the interaction between the state and the UI
